%% WSS 模式端到端数据流 (纯 WebSocket 中继, 无 WireGuard)
%% 用途: 受限网络下的回退路径, 使用自定义 WsFrame 协议承载 TCP/UDP 流
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User App
    participant NSC as NSC
    participant GW as NSGW<br/>(traefik :443 WSS Relay)
    participant WS as tunnel-ws<br/>(NSN WsFrame codec)
    participant ACL as ACL Engine
    participant SR as ServiceRouter
    participant PX as Proxy
    participant SVC as Service

    U->>NSC: connect("ssh.ab3xk9mnpq.n.ns:22")
    NSC->>GW: TLS 1.3 + WSS<br/>WsFrame Open{port=22, proto=tcp, fqid}
    GW->>WS: WSS 中继至 NSN (WsFrame)

    WS->>ACL: check(target port + proto)
    alt ACL 拒绝
        ACL-->>WS: deny
        WS-->>GW: WsFrame Close + 错误码
    else ACL 通过
        ACL->>SR: resolve(service)
        SR->>PX: target = 127.0.0.1:22
        PX->>SVC: TCP connect
        loop 数据交换
            NSC->>GW: WsFrame Data{payload}
            GW->>WS: 透传 WsFrame Data
            WS->>PX: 写 payload
            PX->>SVC: 转发字节
            SVC-->>PX: 回复
            PX-->>WS: 字节
            WS-->>GW: WsFrame Data{reply}
            GW-->>NSC: WSS 数据帧
        end
        NSC->>GW: WsFrame Close
        GW->>WS: WsFrame Close
        WS->>PX: close
    end
